Can you speak with an English accent?
Your answer to that question might depend on what your definition of “English” is, since there are so many dialects of the English language.&nbsp;
Two of the most common types are American and British English. While they’re both technically the same language, there are tons of differences between the two.&nbsp;
In this article, we’re going to look at the British accent vs. the American accent.
